                                                                                                                     rdfs:comment "References the MARPOL-specific waste passport subject (`MarpolWastePassport`)." .


###  https://blue-room-innovation.github.io/bri-ontology/ontology/v0.1/digitalMarpolWastePassport.ttl#estimatedGenerated
<https://blue-room-innovation.github.io/bri-ontology/ontology/v0.1/digitalMarpolWastePassport.ttl#estimatedGenerated> rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty ;
