<https://blue-room-innovation.github.io/bri-ontology/ontology/v0.1/digitalMarpolWastePassport.ttl#maxCapacity> rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty ;
                                                                                                               rdfs:domain <https://blue-room-innovation.github.io/bri-ontology/ontology/v0.1/digitalMarpolWastePassport.ttl#ResidueInformation> ;
                                                                                                               rdfs:range <https://ontology.untp.io/core/Measure> ;
                                                                                                               rdfs:comment "The maximum capacity for residue storage, represented as a measure." .


###  https://blue-room-innovation.github.io/bri-ontology/ontology/v0.1/digitalMarpolWastePassport.ttl#message
<https://blue-room-innovation.github.io/bri-ontology/ontology/v0.1/digitalMarpolWastePassport.ttl#message> rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty ;
