###  https://blue-room-innovation.github.io/bri-ontology/ontology/v0.1/digitalMarpolWastePassport.ttl#quantityToDeliver
<https://blue-room-innovation.github.io/bri-ontology/ontology/v0.1/digitalMarpolWastePassport.ttl#quantityToDeliver> rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty ;
                                                                                                                     rdfs:domain <https://blue-room-innovation.github.io/bri-ontology/ontology/v0.1/digitalMarpolWastePassport.ttl#ResidueInformation> ;
                                                                                                                     rdfs:range <https://ontology.untp.io/core/Measure> ;
                                                                                                                     rdfs:comment "The quantity of residue to be delivered, represented as a measure." .


###  https://blue-room-innovation.github.io/bri-ontology/ontology/v0.1/digitalMarpolWastePassport.ttl#residue
<https://blue-room-innovation.github.io/bri-ontology/ontology/v0.1/digitalMarpolWastePassport.ttl#residue> rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty ;
                                                                                                           rdfs:domain <https://blue-room-innovation.github.io/bri-ontology/ontology/v0.1/digitalMarpolWastePassport.ttl#MarpolWaste> ;
                                                                                                           rdfs:range <https://blue-room-innovation.github.io/bri-ontology/ontology/v0.1/digitalMarpolWastePassport.ttl#ResidueInformation> ;
                                                                                                           rdfs:comment "Detailed information about the waste residue, including type, quantity, and discharge method." .


###  https://blue-room-innovation.github.io/bri-ontology/ontology/v0.1/digitalMarpolWastePassport.ttl#role
<https://blue-room-innovation.github.io/bri-ontology/ontology/v0.1/digitalMarpolWastePassport.ttl#role> rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty ;
