###  https://blue-room-innovation.github.io/bri-ontology/codelists/v0.1/delivery-type-code.ttl#DeliveryTypeCodeScheme
<https://blue-room-innovation.github.io/bri-ontology/codelists/v0.1/delivery-type-code.ttl#DeliveryTypeCodeScheme> rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                                                                                                                            <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#ConceptScheme> ;
                                                                                                                   rdfs:comment "Defines delivery types for MARPOL waste, indicating how waste is collected, recycled, or discharged at port reception facilities."@en ;
                                                                                                                   <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A code that specifies the type of delivery for ship-generated waste, as defined by a local codelist."@en ;
                                                                                                                   <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#note> "Linked to the property :deliveryType in the Digital MARPOL Waste Passport ontology, constraining allowed values to this controlled vocabulary."@en ;
                                                                                                                   <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Delivery Type Code"@en .


###  https://blue-room-innovation.github.io/bri-ontology/codelists/v0.1/delivery-type-code.ttl#REC
