                                                                                                         <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#Concept> ;
                                                                                                <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Recycled waste."@en ;
                                                                                                <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#inScheme> <https://blue-room-innovation.github.io/bri-ontology/codelists/v0.1/delivery-type-code.ttl#DeliveryTypeCodeScheme> ;
