                                                                                                <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "ZTO"@en .


###  https://blue-room-innovation.github.io/bri-ontology/codelists/v0.1/discharge-means-code.ttl#DischargeMeansCodeScheme
<https://blue-room-innovation.github.io/bri-ontology/codelists/v0.1/discharge-means-code.ttl#DischargeMeansCodeScheme> rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                                                                                                                                <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#ConceptScheme> ;
                                                                                                                       rdfs:comment "Defines the possible discharge methods under MARPOL waste handling processes."@en ;
                                                                                                                       <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A code that specifies the means or method of discharge for a particular residue or waste material."@en ;
                                                                                                                       <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#note> "Linked to the property :dischargeMeans in the Digital MARPOL Waste Passport ontology, constraining allowed values to this controlled vocabulary."@en ;
                                                                                                                       <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Discharge Means Code"@en .


###  https://blue-room-innovation.github.io/bri-ontology/codelists/v0.1/discharge-means-code.ttl#ZTB
