                                                                                                  <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#inScheme> <https://blue-room-innovation.github.io/bri-ontology/codelists/v0.1/discharge-means-code.ttl#DischargeMeansCodeScheme> ;
                                                                                                  <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "ZTD"@en .


