                                                                                                                 <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#note> "Linked to the property :typeCode in the Digital MARPOL Waste Passport ontology, constraining allowed values to this controlled vocabulary."@en ;
                                                                                                                 <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Residue Type Code"@en .


